{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781518851063,"sessionID":"ses_13537258affeVXgYvTahskeLzp","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"tool_pJfRNvuExCcHA70sjFzmyk0c","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"---\ntitle: Deep Research Dashboard - Fable-5 Efficiency (kimi-k2p7)\ndescription: Auto-generated session overview for the kimi-k2p7 fan-out lineage.\nimportance_tier: normal\ncontextType: general\n---\n\n# Deep Research Dashboard - Fable-5 Efficiency (kimi-k2p7)\n\n## 2. STATUS\n- Topic: Fable-5 efficiency — map every adjustable Public-repo surface and optimization from fable-mode-main and opus-fable-mode-main sources, deduped against round 1\n- Started: 2026-06-15T12:17:00Z\n- Status: INITIALIZED\n- Iteration: 0 of 5\n- Session ID: fanout-kimi-k2p7-1781518620710-yepc7q\n- Parent Session: none\n- Lifecycle Mode: new\n- Generation: 1\n\n## 3. PROGRESS\n\n| # | Focus | Track | Ratio | Findings | Status |\n|---|-------|-------|-------|----------|--------|\n\n- iterationsCompleted: 0\n- keyFindings: 0\n- openQuestions: 5\n- resolvedQuestions: 0\n\n## 4. QUESTIONS\n- Answered: 0/5\n- [ ] Q1: What net-new fable-5 techniques/rituals/mechanisms/measurements exist in fable-mode-main and opus-fable-mode-main vs Fable5.md and round 1?\n- [ ] Q2: What adjustable Public-repo surfaces exist and what is their read-reliability per runtime?\n- [ ] Q3: Which surface×delta recommendations are highest leverage/lowest blast-radius, tiered A/B/C, deduped vs round 1?\n- [ ] Q4: What concrete measurement surface can host a leak_test-style behavioral metric?\n- [ ] Q5: What are the risks, dependencies, and open questions for the top recommendations?\n\n## 5. TREND\n- Last 3 ratios: —\n- Stuck count: 0\n- Guard violations: none\n\n## 6. DEAD ENDS\n- none yet\n\n## 7. NEXT FOCUS\nIteration 1: Systematically extract net-new mechanisms from `fable-mode-main/fable-mode.md` and `fable-mode-profile.md`, tagging each as doctrine/ritual/mechanism/measurement/model-specific and checking against Fable5.md + round 1.\n\n## 8. ACTIVE RISKS\n- none yet\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/149-operate-like-fable-5/002-fable-mode-efficiency-research/research/lineages/kimi-k2p7/deep-research-dashboard.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/149-operate-like-fable-5/002-fable-mode-efficiency-research/research/lineages/kimi-k2p7/deep-research-dashboard.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/149-operate-like-fable-5/002-fable-mode-efficiency-research/research/lineages/kimi-k2p7/deep-research-dashboard.md","time":{"start":1781518851058,"end":1781518851062}},"id":"prt_ecacc325c001dslBFbw8rSVRvl","sessionID":"ses_13537258affeVXgYvTahskeLzp","messageID":"msg_ecacbfaa7001H5BNJiKkPj9Wrg"}}
