 \"Run phase_synthesis: write lineage research.md\",\n    \"status\": \"pending\",\n    \"priority\": \"high\"\n  }\n]","metadata":{"todos":[{"content":"Run phase_init: create lineage config, strategy, state, registry, dashboard","status":"completed","priority":"high"},{"content":"Iteration 1: Extract net-new mechanisms from fable-mode-main","status":"completed","priority":"high"},{"content":"Iteration 2: Extract net-new mechanisms from opus-fable-mode-main","status":"in_progress","priority":"high"},{"content":"Iteration 3: Map adjustable Public-repo surfaces and read-reliability","status":"pending","priority":"high"},{"content":"Iteration 4: Build ranked/tiered/deduped recommendation map","status":"pending","priority":"high"},{"content":"Iteration 5: Measurement surface and final gap check","status":"pending","priority":"high"},{"content":"Run phase_synthesis: write lineage research.md","status":"pending","priority":"high"}],"truncated":false},"title":"5 todos","time":{"start":1781519044999,"end":1781519045000}},"id":"prt_ecacf46860013Y4jAr9MMFWBtR","sessionID":"ses_13537258affeVXgYvTahskeLzp","messageID":"msg_ecacf1f2e001feTp8HaYg1P4Ny"}}
