sks, dependencies, and open questions for the top recommendations?\n\n## 5. TREND\n- Last 3 ratios: 0.88 -> 0.82 -> 0.65 (declining)\n- Stuck count: 0\n- Guard violations: none\n\n## 6. DEAD ENDS\n- `fable-mode-main/README.md` is install-only; no doctrine to extract.\n- `fable-mode.md` command overlay is self-contained; no hidden mechanisms beyond the profile.\n- `opus-fable-mode-main/reinject.sh` is a deployment helper, not a mechanism.\n- `opus-fable-mode-main/README.md` is install-only.\n- `opus-fable-mode-main/LICENSE` is not relevant to research.\n- `.opencode/commands/create/*.md` are scaffolding templates; not suitable for behavioral governor injection.\n- `Barter/ai-speckit/coder/AGENTS.md` git-posture contradiction needs owner resolution.\n\n## 7. NEXT FOCUS\nIteration 4: Build the ranked, tiered, deduped surface×delta recommendation map. Score each candidate by leverage / (cost + blast-radius), assign Tier A/B/C, and map to the best surface from iteration 3.\n\n## 8. ACTIVE RISKS\n- Trend is declining (0.88 → 0.82 → 0.65); expected as research shifts from extraction to synthesis. Convergence not yet triggered.\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/149-operate-like-fable-5/002-fable-mode-efficiency-research/research/lineages/kimi-k2p7/deep-research-dashboard.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/149-operate-like-fable-5/002-fable-mode-efficiency-research/research/lineages/kimi-k2p7/deep-research-dashboard.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/149-operate-like-fable-5/002-fable-mode-efficiency-research/research/lineages/kimi-k2p7/deep-research-dashboard.md","time":{"start":1781519418344,"end":1781519418350}},"id":"prt_ecad4cc740018cgGyYsuqeIqhB","sessionID":"ses_13537258